remarks: Dedispersed dynamic spectra without (top left) and with (bottom left) zero-DM filtering. Top right: S/N vs DM of grouped events (black dots in the bottom right panel). DM of single pulse detections as a function of time, where the size of the dots scales with S/N. Single pulse events selected by the grouping algorithm that are associated to FRB 200125 are shown in black, while all other events for that DM range are in grey.
